{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"EventTarget","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>dispatchEvent()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>removeEventListener()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>EventTarget</code> é uma interface DOM implementada por objetos que podem receber eventos DOM e tem que ouvir estes.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a>, e <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a> são os mais comuns disparadores de eventos, mas outros objetos podem disparar eventos também, por exemplo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AudioNode\"><code>AudioNode</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AudioContext\"><code>AudioContext</code></a> e outros.</p>\n\n<p>Muitos disparadores de eventos (incluindo elements, documents,&nbsp; e windows) também suportam definir <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/DOM/Events/Event_handlers\">event handlers</a> através <code>on...</code> propriedades e atributos.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"eventtarget.addeventlistener\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Registra um tratamento para um tipo específico de evento sobre o <code>EventTarget</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"eventtarget.removeeventlistener\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.removeEventListener()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Remove um <em>event listener</em> do <code>EventTarget</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"eventtarget.dispatchevent\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>EventTarget.dispatchEvent()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Dispatch an event to this <code>EventTarget</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-eventtarget\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'EventTarget' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Sem mundanças.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2014/WD-DOM-Level-3-Events-20140925/DOM3-Events.html#interface-EventTarget\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 3 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'EventTarget' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>Alguns parâmetros agora são opcionais (<code>listener</code>), ou aceitam o valor <code>null</code> (<code>useCapture</code>).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.htmlevents.html#Events-EventTarget\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'EventTarget' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Funcionalidade</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>7</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Funcionalidade</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>1.0 (1)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>6.0</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"additional_methods_for_mozilla_chrome_code","title":"Additional methods for Mozilla chrome code","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Mozilla extensions for use by JS-implemented event targets to implement on* properties. See also <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/WebIDL_bindings\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">WebIDL bindings</a>.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>void <strong>setEventHandler</strong>(DOMString type, EventHandler handler) <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n <li>EventHandler <strong>getEventHandler</strong>(DOMString type) <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Events\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">Referência de eventos (en-US)</a> - os eventos disponíveis na plataforma.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Guide/DOM/Events\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Guia do desenvolvedor sobre Eventos</a></li>\n <li>Interface <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Métodos","id":"methods"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specification"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"EventTarget é uma interface DOM implementada por objetos que podem receber eventos DOM e tem que ouvir estes.","popularity":0.001,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"EventTarget","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/eventtarget","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/eventtarget/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget","title":"EventTarget"}],"pageTitle":"EventTarget - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}